{"tid":1361236,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[理性分析] 7.27行動方案","createTime":"2019-07-24T14:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T16:44:00.000Z","uid":273207,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f726aa5ac9f406f16d2610f9e3cf1f5fcf883e54","tid":1361236,"uid":273207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:21:55.000Z","msg":"呢件事好重要！請幫手推！<br />\n<br />\n我可以好肯定咁講:<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「衝入村，燒祠堂一定輸！」</span></strong></span>，記往以下幾點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 遊行一定要對準<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>政權</strong></span>，對準<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗黑警</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2. 黑社會都<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>只係收錢做野</strong></span>，而<strong>比錢黑社會既都係<span style=\"color: red;\">政權</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n3. 政府搵得黑社會，證明佢地都無乜招，<br />\n而家佢地<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唯一招數</span>係搵「鬼」7.27搞事</strong></span>，<br />\n刺激我地傷害平民同燒祠堂，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">令民意逆轉</span></strong>，<br />\n所以我地<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一定唔可以中計</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n4. 如果真係衝入村同燒祠堂，或者傷到鄉民，<br />\n我地做既野<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同7.21元朗恐襲無分別！</span></span></strong> <br />\n我地之前既和平行動就會<strong>一鋪清袋</strong><br />\n (呢個<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">世界係好鐘意將人既污點放大</span></strong>，媒體都係)<br />\n<br />\n5. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好比任何人搞事</span></span></strong>，衝入村或者燒祠堂（無論係咪「鬼」都好）<br />\n每次遊行都一定有「鬼」帶頭搞事，<br />\n前幾次都無所謂，但今次好重要。(因為會<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有機會傷到平民</span></strong>)<br />\n而「鬼」既特色係帶動左啲人搞事，<br />\n然後<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「鬼」自己會最快撒離現場</span></strong>，等其他勇武兄弟衝。<br />\n<br />\n6. 一定要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">守住我地之前咁多行動建立左既民意</span></strong>，<br />\n比全世界見到我地香港人可以<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>好齊心，好和平</strong></span>咁表達意見！<br />\n就算政府砌我地係「暴徒」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">國際媒體都會睇到我地架!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n記住，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政權</span></span></strong>同<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">元朗黑警</span></strong></span>先係我地既目標！"},{"pid":"dcf91ae4c6c16c0a0f3431077110fd742a834b21","tid":1361236,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:22:57.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">《生於亂世，有種責任》</span></span><br />\n唔好意思阻阻大家，我地想幫香港人出書，想收集大家意見<br />\n<br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cb3f5fd8a1103076101d1c8617c10f391d04be91","tid":1361236,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:30:25.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"400e369c3f9f7cb64362da77a3fe26c17982f15d","tid":1361236,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借一借位<br />\n<br />\n投時間<br />\n<br />\n【最新進展】元朗遊行官方時間無得提早<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1360015</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2a1926a73eec80bd2a1060378b3cd2d151251645","tid":1361236,"uid":279636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6852b951cc3bfddf089e2b84af7565ce4e4fdf0","tid":1361236,"uid":269965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1ca39cb14cc6299b6984d3c1d79aad436a8b4647","tid":1361236,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:41:12.000Z","m